title: Christian Siriano
itunes:title: Christian Siriano
itunes:subtitle: CHRISTIAN SIRIANO (Project Runway) joins Anna to discuss dressing up, muses and inspiration, fashion week, first heartbreak, vanity and more. Anna and Christian then give Unqualified advice to callers Jamon and Alex. This will be the last Unqualified epis
description:
In this episode...

- An invite to Fashion Week
- Dressing up
- Christian’s Muses
- Musicals
- Pink vs. yellow
- Playing a character
- First heartbreak
- Applying for an internship
- Male vs. Female Vanity
- Advice to callers Jamon and Alex
